i.png?m=1568872887", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 274403}, "last_reply_by": "MCyunpeng98", "last_touched": 1634118786, "title": "为什么国内做不出开发工具？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/807502", "created": 1634095089, "content": "比如 idea,eclipse,navicat,包括文本编辑器等等。\r\n或者说是有些领域是有比较好的工具，我孤陋寡闻了？\r\n\r\n抛开如\"容易被破解不赚钱\"这种说法，那些软件一直被破解但还是在做不是么。", "content_rendered": "比如 idea,eclipse,navicat,包括文本编辑器等等。<br />或者说是有些领域是有比较好的工具，我孤陋寡闻了？<br /><br />抛开如\"容易被破解不赚钱\"这种说法，那些软件一直被破解但还是在做不是么。", "last_modified": 1634095089, "replies": 74, "id": 807502}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1633245702", "name": "security", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1633245702", "title": "信息安全", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/security", "topics": 1238, "footer": "", "header": "我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。", "title_alternative": "Security", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1633245702", "stars": 1366, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 260, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"username": "balabalaguguji", "website": "https://tools.fun", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1383/cc45/341424_mini.png?m=1565918639", "bio": "创业者，工具箱：https://tools.fun，SVN托管：https://svnbucket.com，API文档、测试：https://easydoc.net", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/balabalaguguji", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1534320435, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1383/cc45/341424_mini.png?m=1565918639", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1383/cc45/341424_mini.png?m=1565918639", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 341424}, "last_reply_by": "podel", "last_touched": 1634119389, "title": "私有部署如何避免代码泄露？如何限制服务有效期？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/807464", "created": 1634089904, "content": "需要给客户部署 web 服务到他们服务器，想给他一个注册码，填入后就可以获得一年有效期，到期后无法使用，就类似 jetbrains 的付费方式。\r\n\r\n但是服务端代码如果是 js/python 这类脚本语言，代码都是明文的，不好做有效期的逻辑，别人直接改掉就没了，有什么办法做到呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>需要给客户部署 web 服务到他们服务器，想给他一个注册码，填入后就可以获得一年有效期，到期后无法使用，就类似 jetbrains 的付费方式。</p>\n<p>但是服务端代码如果是 js/python 这类脚本语言，代码都是明文的，不好做有效期的逻辑，别人直接改掉就没了，有什么办法做到呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1634093312, "replies": 56, "id": 807464}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933", "name": "mbp", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933", "title": "MacBook Pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp", "topics": 7185, "footer": "", "header": "State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.", "title_alternative": "MacBook Pro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933", "stars": 2940, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 10, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "Rickyyyy", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cca/8e25/501247_mini.png?m=1609291957", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Rickyyyy", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1595943895, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cca/8e25/501247_mini.png?m=1609291957", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cca/8e25/501247_mini.png?m=1609291957", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 501247}, "last_reply_by": "violetlai", "last_touched": 1634119060, "title": "有没有什么擦 mbp 屏幕特别好的布，用过眼睛布什么的 不好用", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/807516", "created": 1634097485, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1634097485, "replies": 56, "id": 807516}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "taobao", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "淘宝", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/taobao", "topics": 289, "footer": null, "header": null, "title_alternative": "淘宝", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 55, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 726, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"username": "toaruScar", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a02a2d80d7ab09138979f497f7401500?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/toaruScar", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1591916321, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a02a2d80d7ab09138979f497f7401500?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a02a2d80d7ab09138979f497f7401500?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 494386}, "last_reply_by": "sonyxperia", "last_touched": 1634116476, "title": "被天猫商家诱导，我愣是把自己的差评给隐藏了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/807441", "created": 1634073242, "content": "\\>在天猫买了一个太阳能灯\r\n\r\n\\>评价了一下，大意是阴雨天会影响晚上的亮度\r\n\r\n\\>客服来找我，说发一段话能退 30 块钱\r\n![对话截图]( https://d.pr/i/UKateq+)\r\n\r\n\\>没多想，发了追评，拿了钱。\r\n\r\n\\>第二天发现评论被折叠\r\n![被折叠的评论]( https://d.pr/i/x5xb9l+)\r\n\r\n\r\n现在才突然明白是怎么回事，卖家花了 30 块钱，就把我这个不好的评价给消除了，而且还投诉无门。\r\n\r\n感觉智商被侮辱了，贪小便宜吃小亏。发上来希望下次大家不要被金钱蒙蔽了双眼。", "content_rendered": "<p>&gt;在天猫买了一个太阳能灯</p>\n<p>&gt;评价了一下，大意是阴雨天会影响晚上的亮度</p>\n<p>&gt;客服来找我，说发一段话能退 30 块钱\n<img alt=\"对话截图\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://d.pr/i/UKateq+\"/></p>\n<p>&gt;没多想，发了追评，拿了钱。</p>\n<p>&gt;第二天发现评论被折叠\n<img alt=\"被折叠的评论\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://d.pr/i/x5xb9l+\"/></p>\n<p>现在才突然明白是怎么回事，卖家花了 30 块钱，就把我这个不好的评价给消除了，而且还投诉无门。</p>\n<p>感觉智商被侮辱了，贪小便宜吃小亏。发上来希望下次大家不要被金钱蒙蔽了双眼。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1634073242, "replies": 47, "id": 807441}]